column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your first quest is to find the long lost Blade of Osiris. This powerful weapon disappeared long ago in the inhospitable landscape around the Castle of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your first quest is to find the long lost Blade of Osiris. This powerful weapon disappeared long ago in the inhospitable landscape around the Castle of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Deine erste Aufgabe ist es, die  verlorene Klinge des Osiris zu finden. Diese mächtige Waffe verschwand vor langer Zeit in der ungastlichen Landschaft um den Palast von Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ta première quête consiste à trouver l'Épée d'Osiris, une arme puissante perdue depuis la nuit des temps dans les environs inhospitaliers du Palais d'Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tu primera misión es encontrar la Espada de Osiris perdida. Esta poderosa arma desapareció hace años en los inhóspitos parajes que rodean el Palacio de Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>La nostra prima missione è trovare la Lama di Osiride, una potente lama perduta molto tempo fa nelle terre ostili attorno al Castello di Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>너의 첫 번째 모험은 오랫동안 분실되었던 오시리스의 검을 찾는 것이다. 이 강력한 무기는 우루크 성의 황폐한 땅에서 오래 전 사라졌다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>最初のクエストは昔に失われたオシリスの剣を見つけること。この強い武器は、大昔ウルク城の不毛な周りに無くなった。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Η πρώτη σου αποστολή είναι να βρεις το χαμένο Σπαθί του Όσιρι. Αυτό το ισχυρό όπλο εξαφανίστηκε πριν πολύ καιρό στο αφιλόξενο τοπίο γύρω από το κάστρο της Ουρούκ.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your first quest is to find the long lost Blade of Osiris. This powerful weapon disappeared long ago in the inhospitable landscape around the Castle of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Sua primeira missão é encontrar a Espada de Osíris. Essa poderosa arma desapareceu há muito tempo atrás nos arredores inóspitos do Castelo de Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrieve Nefertiti's Letter and return it to her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrieve Nefertiti's Letter and return it to her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Hole Nefertitis Brief und bringe ihn zu ihr.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Récupère la Lettre de Néfertiti et rends-la lui.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Recupera la carta de Nefertiti y entrégasela.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova la Lettera di Nefertiti e riportala a lei.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>네퍼르티티의 편지를 회수하여 그녀에게 돌려주어라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ネフェルティティの手紙を取り出して返す。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ανάκτησε το Γράμμα της Νεφερτίτης και επίστρεψε το σε αυτήν.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrieve Nefertiti's Letter and return it to her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Recupere a carta de Nefertiti e devolva-a para ela.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Collect the 8 Old Amulets and return them to your Aunt Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Collect the 8 Old Amulets and return them to your Aunt Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Sammle die 8 alten Amulette und bringe sie deiner Tante Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ramasse 8 Vieilles Amulettes et rends-les à ta Tante Séti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Reúne los 8 amuletos antiguos y devuélveselos a tía Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Raccogli gli 8 Vecchi Amuleti e riportali a tua zia Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>8개의 오래된 부적들을 수집하여 숙모 세티에게 돌려주어라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>古いお守りを8つ集めて、セティ叔母さんに返す。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Σύλλεξε τα 8 Παλιά Φυλαχτά και επίστρεψε τα στη Σέτι, τη θεία σου.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Collect the 8 Old Amulets and return them to your Aunt Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Colete os 8 Amuletos Antigos e os retorne para sua tia Seti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Once you have used the Abydos Amulet, Imhotep wants you to seek transport to Heliopolis and meet up with him as soon as possible.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Once you have used the Abydos Amulet, Imhotep wants you to seek transport to Heliopolis and meet up with him as soon as possible.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep möchte, dass du nach Heliopolis reist, nachdem du das Abydosamulett benutzt hast. Dort sollst du dich so schnell wie möglich mit ihm treffen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>L'Amulette d'Abydos utilisée, Imhotep te demande de te rendre à Héliopolis pour le rejoindre au plus vite.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Después de utilizar el Amuleto de Abydos, Imhotep quiere que busques transporte hasta Heliópolis y que te reúnas con él lo antes posible.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Dopo aver usato l'Amuleto di Abydos, Imhotep vuole che tu cerchi un mezzo di trasporto per Heliopolis e lo incontri al più presto.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아비도스 부적을 한 번 사용하면, 임호텝은 네가 최대한 빨리 헬리오폴리스로 가는 전송장치를 찾아서 그를 만나기를 원한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アビドスのお守りを使った後、急いでヘリオポリスへの行く方法を探す。イムホテプはスフィンクスにまた会いたい。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Μόλις χρησιμοποιήσεις το Φυλαχτό της Αβύδου, ο Ιμχοτέπ θέλει να βρεις μεταφορικό μέσο για την Ηλιούπολη και να συναντηθείς μαζί του το συντομότερο δυνατόν.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Once you have used the Abydos Amulet, Imhotep wants you to seek transport to Heliopolis and meet up with him as soon as possible.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Quando você tiver usado o Amuleto de Abydos, Imhotep quer que você busque transporte para Heliópolis e encontre com ele assim que possível.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find 3 Pearls and give them to the Abydosian man.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find 3 Pearls and give them to the Abydosian man.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde 3 Perlen und gib sie dem abydosianischen Mann.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trouve 3 Perles et donne-les à l'Abydosien.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca 3 perlas y dáselas al hombre de Abydos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova 3 perle e dalle all'uomo di Abydos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>3개의 진주를 찾아서 그 아비도스 남자에게 준다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>真珠を3つ集めてアビドスの男に届ける。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες 3 Πέρλες και δώσ' τες στον άνδρα από την Άβυδο.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find 3 Pearls and give them to the Abydosian man.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre 3 Pérolas e dê elas ao homem Abydosiano.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Curator of Abydos Museum is offering a gift when you make your first donation.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Curator of Abydos Museum is offering a gift when you make your first donation.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Der Kurator des Museums von Abydos gibt dir ein Geschenk, sobald du deine erste Spende machst.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le Conservateur du Musée d'Abydos te fait un cadeau à la première donation.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>El conservador del Museo de Abydos te dará un regalo cuando hagas la primera donación.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Il curatore del Museo di Abydos ti offrirà un regalo per la tua prima donazione.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아비도스 박물관의 관장이 네가 첫 번째 기증을 하면 선물을 줄 것이다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アビドス博物館に初めて寄付をすると、アビドス博物館のキュレーターは贈り物をする。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ο έφορος του Μουσείου της Αβύδου προσφέρει ένα δώρο όταν κάνεις την πρώτη σου δωρεά.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Curator of Abydos Museum is offering a gift when you make your first donation.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>O Curador do Museu de Abydos está oferecendo um presente quando você fizer sua primeira doação.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guards in Abydos Canal will not allow access to the Council Chambers. Perhaps you should return to Abydos later in your quest when you have suitable identification.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guards in Abydos Canal will not allow access to the Council Chambers. Perhaps you should return to Abydos later in your quest when you have suitable identification.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Die Wachen beim Abydos Kanal verweigern dir den Zutritt zu den Ratskammern. Vielleicht solltest du später wiederkommen, wenn du eine geeignete Identifikation hast.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Les Gardes du Canal d'Abydos interdisent l'accès à la Salle du Conseil. Tu devrais revenir plus tard, dans ta quête, lorsque tu auras l'autorisation requise.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>La guardia del Canal de Abydos no te permitirá el acceso al Consistorio. Quizás debas volver a Abydos más adelante, cuando tengas la identificación apropiada.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le guardie del Canale di Abydos non permettono di entrare nelle Camere del Consiglio. Forse dovresti tornare ad Abydos più avanti, munito di un documento adatto.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아비도스 운하의 수비병들이 의회실로 접근을 금지할 것이다. 만약 모험을 하다가 나중에 알맞은 증명서가 있다면 아비도스로 돌아오는 것이 좋을 것이다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アビドス運河の警備員は会議室に入らせてくれない。クエスト中で適当な身分証明書を手に入れる時、アビドスに帰ったほうがいい。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Οι φρουροί του Καναλιού της Αβύδου δεν επιτρέπουν την πρόσβαση στην αίθουσα συνεδριάσεων του συμβουλίου. Ίσως πρέπει να επιστρέψεις στην Άβυδο αργότερα όταν θα έχεις τα κατάλληλα έγγραφα.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guards in Abydos Canal will not allow access to the Council Chambers. Perhaps you should return to Abydos later in your quest when you have suitable identification.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Os Guardas no Canal de Abydos não permitem o acesso às Câmaras do Conselho. Talvez você deva retornar para Abydos mais tarde em sua jornada, quando possuir uma identificação adequada.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep can be found on Sun Shrine Island. Visit him and find out what information he has for you.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep can be found on Sun Shrine Island. Visit him and find out what information he has for you.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep ist auf der Sonnenschreininsel. Besuche ihn dort, denn er hat Informationen für dich.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep se trouve sur l'Île du Temple solaire. Va le voir, il a des informations pour toi.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Puedes encontrar a Imhotep en la Isla del Santuario Solar. Visítalo y te dará información.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep si trova sull'Isola del tempio del sole. Fagli visita e scopri quali informazioni ha per te.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>임호텝은 태양 성당 섬에서 찾을 수 잇다. 그를 방문하여 무슨 정보를 가지고 있는 지 확인하라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>イムホテプは太陽宮島にいる。そこに行って、イムホテプに相談する。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Μπορείς να βρεις τον Ιμχοτέπ στο Νησί του Ναού του Ήλιου. Επισκέψου τον και ανακάλυψε τι πληροφορίες έχει για σένα.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep can be found on Sun Shrine Island. Visit him and find out what information he has for you.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep pode ser encontrado na ilha do Santuário do Sol. Visite-o e descubra que informação ele tem para você.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the Book of the Dead so you can summon Bas-Ket when you find a Canopic Vase. Imhotep believes the book is being held in the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the Book of the Dead so you can summon Bas-Ket when you find a Canopic Vase. Imhotep believes the book is being held in the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde das Buch der Toten, damit du Tragek-Orb beschwören kannst, sobald du eine Urne gefunden hast. Imhotep glaubt, dass das Buch sich im Verfluchten Palast befindet.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cherche le Livre des Morts pour invoquer Khorb-Èye quand tu trouves un Vase canope. Imhotep pense qu'il est dans le Palais maudit.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca el Libro de los Muertos para invocar a Kan-Asta cuando encuentres un Canope. Imhotep cree que el libro se halla en el Palacio Maldito.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova il Libro dei Morti per evocare Bas-Ket quando avrai trovato un Vaso canopo. Imhotep crede che il libro si trovi nel Palazzo maledetto.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>납골단지를 찾았을 때 바스-켓을 소환할 수 있게 사자의 서를 찾아라. 임호텝은 그 책이 저주 받은 성안에 보관되어 있다고 믿는다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>カノポス壺を見つけた時にバス・ケットを召喚できる為に、死者の書を探さなければならない。イムホテプによると死者の書は呪われた宮殿にある。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες το Βιβλίο των Νεκρών ώστε να μπορείς να καλέσεις τον Καλ-Άθι όταν βρεις ένα Κανωπικό Αγγείο. Ο Ιμχοτέπ πιστεύει ότι το Βιβλίο βρίσκεται στο καταραμένο παλάτι.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the Book of the Dead so you can summon Bas-Ket when you find a Canopic Vase. Imhotep believes the book is being held in the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre o Livro dos Mortos para que você possa invocar Ces-To quando encontrar um Vaso Canópico. Imhotep acredita que o livro está sendo mantido no Palácio Amaldiçoado.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis is responsible for cursing the inhabitants of the Cursed Palace. With the Wings of Ibis you can enter Great Wall Entrance I, and pay a visit to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis is responsible for cursing the inhabitants of the Cursed Palace. With the Wings of Ibis you can enter Great Wall Entrance I, and pay a visit to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis hat die Bewohner des Verfluchten Palastes verdammt. Mit den Flügeln des Ibis kannst du den Eingang I der Großen Mauer passieren und Anubis besuchen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis a maudit les habitants du Palais maudit. Avec les Ailes d'Ibis, tu peux passer par l'Entrée I du Mur pour rendre visite à Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis es responsable de la maldición de los habitantes del Palacio Maldito. Con las Alas de Ibis puedes atravesar la Puerta del Muro I y visitar a Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubi è l'autore della maledizione agli abitanti del Palazzo maledetto. Con le Ali di Ibis puoi attraversare l'Entrata della Grande Muraglia I e raggiungerlo.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아누비스가 저주 받은 성의 주민들이 저주 받은 것에 관한 책임이 있다. 이비스의 날개로 벽 입구 I로 들어가서 아누비스를 만날 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>呪われた宮殿の住民を呪ったのはアヌビスだ。アイビスの翼を使えば長城入口1に入ってアヌビスに訪問できる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ο Άνουβις ευθύνεται για την κατάρα των κατοίκων του Καταραμένου Παλατιού. Με τα φτερά της Ίβιδας μπορείς να μπεις στην Είσοδο του Τείχους Ι και να επισκεφτείς τον Άνουβι.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anubis is responsible for cursing the inhabitants of the Cursed Palace. With the Wings of Ibis you can enter Great Wall Entrance I, and pay a visit to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Anúbis é o responsável por amaldiçoar os habitantes do Palácio Amaldiçoado. Com as Asas de Ibis você pode entrar na Entrada da Grande Muralha I e fazer uma visita a Anúbis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture 3 Fire Armadillos using Capture Beetles and bring them to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture 3 Fire Armadillos using Capture Beetles and bring them to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Fange 3 Feuergürteltiere mit Fangkäfern und bringe sie zu Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture 3 Tatous de feu avec des Insectes chasseurs. Apporte-les à Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Captura 3 Armadillos de fuego con Escarabajos de captura y dáselos a Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Prendi 3 Armadilli di fuoco con i Coleotteri da cattura e portali ad Anubi.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>화염 아르마딜로들 3마리를 포획 딱정벌레을 사용하여 포획하고 아누비스에게 가져오라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>掴みビートルを使用して炎のアルマジロを3匹掴み、アヌビスに届ける。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Αιχμαλώτισε 3 Αρμαντίλλο της Φωτιάς χρησιμοποιώντας Σκαθάρια Αιχμαλώτισης και φερ' τα στον Άνουβι.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture 3 Fire Armadillos using Capture Beetles and bring them to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture 3 Tatus de Fogo usando Besouros de Captura e leve-os até Anúbis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Farmer's Brother invited you to visit their farm in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Farmer's Brother invited you to visit their farm in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Der Bruder des Bauern hat dich auf den Hof in Heliopolis eingeladen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le Frère du Fermier t'a invité à passer à la ferme d'Héliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>El hermano del granjero te ha invitado a ver su granja en Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Il fratello del fattore ti ha invitato alla loro fattoria a Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>농부의 형제가 너를 헬리오폴리스에 있는 그들의 농장으로 초대했다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>農家のお兄さんは彼らのヘリオポリスにあるファームに招待した。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ο αδερφός του αγρότη σε προσκάλεσε να επισκεφτείς το αγρόκτημα τους στην Ηλιούπολη.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Farmer's Brother invited you to visit their farm in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>O irmão do Fazendeiro o convidou para visitar sua fazenda em Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find where the Nomad's Wife is being held and rescue her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find where the Nomad's Wife is being held and rescue her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde heraus, wo die Frau des Nomaden gefangen ist und rette sie.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrouve l'Épouse du Nomade et sauve-la.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca dónde está retenida la esposa del nómada y rescátala.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Scopri dov'è prigioniera la moglie del nomade e liberala.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>유목민의 아내가 어디에 갇혀있는지를 찾아서 구출하라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>旅人の奥さんを見つけて助ける。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες που είναι κρατούμενη η γυναίκα του νομά και σώσε την.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find where the Nomad's Wife is being held and rescue her.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre onde a esposa do Nômade está sendo mantida e a resgate.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The forcefield imprisoning the Nomad's Wife seems to be powered by three colored beams. Find a way to disable them.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The force field imprisoning the Nomad's Wife seems to be powered by three coloured beams. Find a way to disable them.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Das Kraftfeld um die Frau des Nomaden scheint von drei farbigen Strahlen erzeugt zu werden. Schalte sie ab.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le champ de force retenant l'Épouse du Nomade est alimenté par trois rayons de couleur. Désactive-les.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>El campo de fuerza que retiene a la esposa del nómada funciona con tres rayos de color. Busca cómo desactivarlos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Il campo di forza che imprigiona la moglie del nomade sembra generato da tre raggi colorati. Scopri come disattivarli.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>유목민의 아내를 가두어두고 있는 장벽이 세 가지의 색상의 광선들에 의해서 힘을 공급 받는 것 같다. 그들을 제거할 수 있는 방법을 찾아라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>旅人の奥さんを閉じ込めるフォースフィールドは三色の光線によって供給されている。消す方法を探す。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Το πεδίο που φυλακίζει τη γυναίκα του νομά φαίνεται να τροφοδοτείται απο τρεις χρωματιστές ακτίνες. Βρες ένα τρόπο να τις απενεργοποιήσεις.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The forcefield imprisoning the Nomad's Wife seems to be powered by three colored beams. Find a way to disable them.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>O campo de força que aprisiona a esposa do Nômade parece ser alimentado por três feixes coloridos. Encontre um meio de desativá-los.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep has requested that you go and speak to him in the Sun Shrine.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep has requested that you go and speak to him in the Sun Shrine.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep bittet dich zu einem Gespräch im Tempel auf der Sonnenschreininsel.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep te demande de te rendre au Temple solaire, il veut te parler.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep te ha pedido que te reúnas con él en el Santuario Solar.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep ti ha chiesto di raggiungere il Tempio del Sole per parlarti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>임호텝이 너에게 태양 성당으로 가서 그와 대화할 것을 요청하였다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>イムホテプは太陽宮に行って、彼と話すことを頼んだ<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ο Ιμχοτέπ ζήτησε να πας και να μιλήσεις μαζί του στο Ναό του Ήλιου.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep has requested that you go and speak to him in the Sun Shrine.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Imhotep solicitou que você vá e fale com ele no Santuário do Sol.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Abydos and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Abydos and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Du musst die Heilige Krone von Abydos finden und sie zu Anubis in Heliopolis bringen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrouve la Couronne sacrée d'Abydos et apporte-la à Anubis, à Héliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encuentra la Corona sagrada de Abydos y devuélvesela a Anubis en Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Devi trovare la Sacra corona di Abydos e riportarla ad Anubi a Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아비도스의 성스러운 관을 찾아서 헬리오폴리스의 아누비스에게 돌려주어야만 한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アビドスの聖なるクラウンを見つけて、ヘリオポリスでアヌビスに返さなきゃいけない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Πρέπει να βρεις το Ιερό Στέμμα της Αβύδου και να το επιστρέψεις στον Άνουβι στην Ηλιούπολη.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Abydos and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você deve encontrar a Coroa Sagrada de Abydos e retorná-la para Anúbis em Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Apparently the Mayor has been taken seriously ill. Perhaps the people in Abydos Council Chambers could use your help.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Apparently the Mayor has been taken seriously ill. Perhaps the people in Abydos Council Chambers could use your help.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Offensichtlich ist der Bürgermeister schwer krank. Vielleicht können die Leute in den Ratskammern von Abydos deine Hilfe gebrauchen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le Maire a l'air très malade. Le Conseil d'Abydos pourrait avoir besoin de ton aide.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Parece que el Gobernador está muy enfermo. Puede que en el Consistorio de Abydos necesiten tu ayuda.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Sembra che il Sindaco sia gravemente ammalato. Forse puoi aiutare i membri delle Camere del Consiglio di Abydos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>분명히 시장은 심각하게 앓고 있다. 아비도스 의회실의 사람들의 너의 도움을 받을 수 있을 것 같다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>市長が大変病気になったらしい。スフィンクスがアビドス会議室に行けば、役に立つかもしれない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Προφανώς ο δήμαρχος αρρώστησε σοβαρά. Οι άνθρωποι που βρίσκονται στην αίθουσα συνεδριάσεων του συμβουλίου μπορεί να χρειαστούν τη βοήθεια σου.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Apparently the Mayor has been taken seriously ill. Perhaps the people in Abydos Council Chambers could use your help.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Aparentemente o Prefeito está seriamente doente. Talvez as pessoas no Conselho de Abydos poderiam usar sua ajuda.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guard near the entrance to the Narrow Canal has offered you a Portal Amulet if you can clear the area of monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guard near the entrance to the Narrow Canal has offered you a Portal Amulet if you can clear the area of monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Die Wache am Kleinen Kanal bietet dir ein Portalamulett, wenn du die Monster in der Gegend beseitigst.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le Garde de l'entrée du Petit Canal t'offre une Amulette de Portail si tu débarrasses le Canal de ses monstres.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>La guardia que custodia la entrada al Pequeño canal te ha ofrecido un Amuleto del portal si limpias la zona de monstruos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>La guardia presso l'entrata del Canale stretto ti ha offerto un Amuleto portale se eliminerai i mostri nella zona.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>소 운하로의 입구 근처에 있는 수비병들이 그 영역에서 괴물들을 제거하면 포털 부적을 주겠다고 제안하였다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>狭い運河にいるモンスターを全部倒すと、入口に立っている警備員にポータルのお守りをもらえるらしい。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ο φρουρός κοντά στην είσοδο του Στενού Καναλιού σου πρόσφερε ένα Φυλαχτό Πύλης αν απομακρύνεις τα τέρατα από την περιοχή.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The Guard near the entrance to the Narrow Canal has offered you a Portal Amulet if you can clear the area of monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>O Guarda próximo à entrada para o Canal Estreito te ofereceu um Amuleto de Portal se você limpar a área dos monstros.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6:
You must find 5 Healing Herbs and bring them to the Physician in the Abydos Council Chambers.

With the herbs the Physician should be able to prepare a cure for the Mayor's mysterious illness.
column7:
You must find 5 Healing Herbs and bring them to the Physician in the Abydos Council Chambers.

With the herbs the Physician should be able to prepare a cure for the Mayor's mysterious illness.
column8:
Du musst 5 Heilkräuter finden und sie zum Arzt in den Ratskammern von Abydos bringen.

Aus den Kräutern kann der Arzt eine Medizin gegen die rätselhafte Krankheit des Bürgermeisters machen.
column9:
Trouve 5 Plantes médicinales et apporte-les au Médecin du Conseil d'Abydos.

Avec ces plantes, le Médecin préparera un remède pour soigner le Maire.
column10:
Busca 5 hierbas medicinales y llévalas al Doctor del Consistorio de Abydos.

Con las hierbas, el Doctor puede preparar una cura para la misteriosa enfermedad del Gobernador.
column11:
Devi trovare 5 Erbe medicinali e portarle al medico nelle Camere del Consiglio di Abydos.

Con queste erbe, il medico dovrebbe preparare una cura per la misteriosa malattia del Sindaco.
column12:
5개의 치료 약초를 찾아서 아비도스 의회실에 있는 의사에게 가져와야만 한다.

그 의사는 약초로 시장의 알 수 없는 병의 치료를 준비할 수 있을 것이다.
column13:
薬草を5つ集めて、アビドス会議室にいる医者に届かなければならない。

薬草があれば、医者は市長の不思議な病気を治すことができるはずだ。
column14:
Πρέπει να βρεις 5 Θεραπευτικά Βότανα και να τα φέρεις στο γιατρό στην αίθουσα συνεδριάσεων του συμβουλίου.

Με τα Βότανα θα μπορέσει ο γιατρός να ετοιμάσει μια θεραπεία για την αρρώστια του δημάρχου.
column15:
You must find 5 Healing Herbs and bring them to the Physician in the Abydos Council Chambers.

With the herbs the Physician should be able to prepare a cure for the Mayor's mysterious illness.
column16:
Você deve encontrar 5 Ervas Medicinais e trazê-las ao médico nas Câmaras do Conselho de Abydos.

Com as ervas o médico deverá ser capaz de preparar uma cura para a doença misteriosa do Prefeito.

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must deliver the Physician's Note to Kemmet, who lives near the Grand Canal. He may be able to help you find the Healing Herbs.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must deliver the Physician's Note to Kemmet, who lives near the Grand Canal. He may be able to help you find the Healing Herbs.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Du musst Kemmet die Notiz des Arztes bringen. Kemmet wohnt am Großen Kanal. Vielleicht kann er dir helfen, die Heilkräuter zu finden.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tu dois donner le message du Médecin à Kemmet, qui habite près du Grand Canal. Il pourra t'aider à trouver les Plantes médicinales.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Debes entregar la nota del Doctor a Kemmet, que vive cerca del Gran canal. Él puede ayudarte a encontrar las hierbas medicinales.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Devi portare l'Appunto del medico a Kemmet, che vive presso il Canale grande. Potrebbe aiutarti a trovare le Erbe medicinali.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>의사의 쪽지를 대 운하 근처에 사는 케메트에게 전달하여야만 한다. 그는 네가 치료 약초를 찾는 것을 도울 수 있을 지도 모른다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>医者のノートをケメットに届かなければいけない。ケメットは盛大運河の周りに住んでいて、薬草を取るのを手伝ってくれるかもしれない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Πρέπει να παραδώσεις το Σημείωμα του Γιατρού στον Κεμμέτ, ο οποίος ζει κοντά στο Μεγάλο Κανάλι. Ίσως να μπορέσει να σε βοηθήσει να βρεις τα θεραπευτικά βότανα.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must deliver the Physician's Note to Kemmet, who lives near the Grand Canal. He may be able to help you find the Healing Herbs.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você deve entregar o bilhete do Médico para Kemmet, que vive próximo ao Grande Canal. Ele pode ser capaz de ajudá-lo a encontrar as Ervas Medicinais.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the traitorous politicians who stole the Sacred Crown of Abydos and win back what is rightfully yours.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the traitorous politicians who stole the Sacred Crown of Abydos and win back what is rightfully yours.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde die verräterischen Politiker und hole dir dein rechtmäßiges Eigentum, die Heilige Krone von Abydos, zurück.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trouve les Traîtres qui ont volé la Couronne sacrée d'Abydos et récupère ce qui te revient de droit.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca a los políticos traidores que robaron la Corona sagrada de Abydos y recupera lo que te pertenece legítimamente.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova i politici traditori che hanno rubato la Sacra corona di Abydos e riprenditi ciò che ti spetta.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아비도스의 성스러운 관을 훔친 배반자 정치인을 찾아서 정당하게 네 것을 되 찾아라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アビドスの聖なるクラウンを盗んだ裏切りの政治家を追いかけて、クラウンを取り戻してやろう。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες τους προδότες πολιτικούς που έκλεψαν το Ιερό Στέμμα της Αβύδου και πάρε πίσω αυτό που σου ανήκει δικαιωματικά.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the traitorous politicians who stole the Sacred Crown of Abydos and win back what is rightfully yours.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre os políticos traidores que roubaram a Coroa Sagrada de Abydos e ganhe de volta o que é seu por direito.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Uruk and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Uruk and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Du musst die Heilige Krone von Uruk finden und sie zu Anubis nach Heliopolis bringen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrouve la Couronne sacrée d'Uruk et apporte-la à Anubis, à Héliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encuentra la Corona sagrada de Uruk y devuélvesela a Anubis en Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Devi trovare la Sacra corona di Uruk e riportarla ad Anubi, a Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>우루크의 성스러운 왕관을 찾아서 헬리오폴리스의 아누비스에게 돌려주어야만 한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ウルクの聖なるクラウンを見つけて、アヌビスに返さなければいけない。（アヌビスはヘリオポリスにいる）<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Πρέπει να βρεις το Ιερό Στέμμα της Ουρούκ και να το επιστρέψεις στον Άνουβι στην Ηλιούπολη.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Uruk and return it to Anubis in Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você deve encontrar a Coroa Sagrada de Uruk e retorná-la para Anúbis em Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the entrance to the Lost Temple of Heliopolis. The Pharaoh's Wife believes that it lies in the South Desert of Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the entrance to the Lost Temple of Heliopolis. The Pharaoh's Wife believes that it lies in the South Desert of Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde den Eingang zum Verschollenen Tempel von Heliopolis. Die Gattin des Pharao vermutet ihn in der Südwüste von Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trouve l'entrée du Temple perdu d'Héliopolis. L'Épouse du Pharaon pense qu'elle se trouve dans le Désert Sud d'Héliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca la entrada del Templo Perdido de Heliópolis. La esposa del Faraón cree que se encuentra en el Desierto Sur de Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova l'entrata del Tempio perduto di Heliopolis. La moglie del Faraone crede che si trovi nel Deserto del Sud di Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>헬리오폴리스의 잊혀진 사원으로 가는 입구를 찾아라. 파라오의 부인은 그것이 헬리오폴리스의 남쪽 사막에 놓여 있다고 믿고 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>失われたヘリオポリスの神殿の入口を見つける。ファラオの奥さんによると南の砂漠にある。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες την είσοδο στο Χαμένο Ναό της Ηλιούπολης. Η γυναίκα του Φαραώ πιστεύει ότι βρίσκεται στη Νότια Έρημο της Ηλιούπολης.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the entrance to the Lost Temple of Heliopolis. The Pharaoh's Wife believes that it lies in the South Desert of Heliopolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre a entrada para o Templo Perdido de Heliópolis. A esposa do Faraó acredita que ele se encontra no Deserto Sul de Heliópolis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the 6 Rosetta Stone Pieces hidden inside the Lost Temple of Heliopolis and bring them to the Archeologist.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the 6 Rosetta Stone Pieces hidden inside the Lost Temple of Heliopolis and bring them to the Archaeologist.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Finde die 6 Teile des Rosettasteins im Verschollenen Tempel von Heliopolis und bringe sie dem Archäologen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trouve les 6 Bouts de Pierre de Rosette cachés dans le Temple perdu d'Héliopolis et donne-les à l'Archéologue.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Busca los 6 trozos de Piedra Rosetta ocultos en el Templo Perdido de Heliópolis y llévalos al Arqueólogo.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Trova i 6 pezzi della Stele di Rosetta nascosti nel Tempio perduto di Heliopolis e portali all'archeologo.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>헬리오폴리스의 잊혀진 사원 안에 숨겨있는 6개의 로제타석 조각들을 찾아서 고고학자에게 가져오라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>失われたヘリオポリスの神殿の中に隠されているロゼッタストーンのかけらを6つ集めて考古学者に届ける。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Βρες τα 6 κομμάτια της Στήλης της Ροζέττας που είναι κρυμμένα στο Χαμένο Ναό της Ηλιούπολης και φερ' τα πίσω στον αρχαιολόγο.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Find the 6 Rosetta Stone Pieces hidden inside the Lost Temple of Heliopolis and bring them to the Archeologist.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encontre as 6 peças da Pedra de Roseta escondidas dentro do Templo Perdido de Heliópolis e traga-as para o Arqueólogo.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Check on the Archeologist's findings in the Bedouin Outpost. The outpost can be found by swimming through the underwater passage from the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Check on the Archaeologist's findings in the Bedouin Outpost. The outpost can be found by swimming through the underwater passage from the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Besuche den Archäologen im Beduinenlager. Dieses kannst du über den Unterwasserweg vom Verfluchten Palast aus erreichen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Jette un œil aux découvertes de l'Archéologue du Camp bédouin. Tu peux y accéder par le passage sous l'eau, depuis le Palais maudit.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Comprueba los hallazgos del Arqueólogo en el Poblado beduino. Puedes llegar al poblado si atraviesas el pasaje sumergido bajo el Palacio Maldito.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Controlla le scoperte dell'archeologo all'Avamposto beduino, che potrai raggiungere superando a nuoto il passaggio subacqueo nel Palazzo maledetto.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>베두인 변방에서 고고학자가 찾은 것들을 확인하라. 전초부대는 저주 받은 성으로부터 수중통로를 통하여 헤엄치면 발견할 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ベドウイン前哨にいる考古学者の研究結果を調べに行く。ベドウイン前哨は呪われた宮殿の周りにある水中通路の向こうにある<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ενημερώσου για τα ευρήματα του αρχαιολόγου στον Καταυλισμό των Βεδουίνων. Μπορείς να βρεις τον καταυλισμό κολυμπώντας μέσα από το υπόγειο πέρασμα από το Καταραμένο Παλάτι.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Check on the Archeologist's findings in the Bedouin Outpost. The outpost can be found by swimming through the underwater passage from the Cursed Palace.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Verifique as descobertas do Arqueólogo no Povoado de Bedouin. O povoado pode ser encontrado nadando pela passagem subaquática do Palácio Amaldiçoado.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Use the Rosetta Stone to translate the 5 Golden Obelisks of Heliopolis and report your findings to the Archeologist in the Bedouin Outpost.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Use the Rosetta Stone to translate the 5 Golden Obelisks of Heliopolis and report your findings to the Archaeologist in the Bedouin Outpost.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Benutze den Rosettastein, um die Texte auf den 5 Goldenen Obelisken von Heliopolis zu übersetzen. Berichte dem Archäologen im Beduinenlager von deinen Erkenntnissen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Traduis les 5 Obélisques d'or d'Héliopolis à l'aide de la Pierre de Rosette et dévoile tes découvertes à l'Archéologue du Camp bédouin.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Usa la Piedra Rosetta para traducir los 5 Obeliscos dorados de Heliópolis y comunica tus hallazgos al Arqueólogo del Poblado beduino.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Usa la Stele di Rosetta per tradurre i 5 Obelischi d'oro di Heliopolis e comunica le tue scoperte all'archeologo nell'Avamposto beduino.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>로제타석을 이용하여 헬리오폴리스의 5개의 황금 오벨리스크들을 해독하고 네가 발견한 것을 베두인 변방에 있는 고고학자에게 보고하라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ロゼッタストーンを使ってヘリオポリスの5つの金色なオベリスクを翻訳して、そしてその情報をベドウイン前哨にいる考古学者に伝える。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Χρησιμοποίησε τη στήλη της Ροζέττας για να μεταφράσεις τους 5 Χρυσούς Οβελίσκους της Ηλιούπολης και ανάφερε τα ευρήματα σου στον αρχαιολόγο στον Καταυλισμό των Βεδουίνων.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Use the Rosetta Stone to translate the 5 Golden Obelisks of Heliopolis and report your findings to the Archeologist in the Bedouin Outpost.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Use a Pedra de Roseta para traduzir os 5 Grandes Obeliscos de Heliópolis e relate seus achados para o Arqueólogo no Povoado de Bedouin.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>When the Age of Osiris comes to an end, the Shadow of Set will descend upon us, but a great warrior by the name of Sphinx, will emerge as the Chosen One, to defend the Eternal Eye of Ra.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>When the Age of Osiris comes to an end, the Shadow of Set will descend upon us, but a great warrior by the name of Sphinx, will emerge as the Chosen One, to defend the Eternal Eye of Ra.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Wenn das Zeitalter des Osiris ein Ende nimmt, wird sich der Schatten von Set über uns senken. Aber ein großer Krieger namens Sphinx wird sich als Auserwählter erweisen, um das Ewige Auge des Ra zu verteidigen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Lorsque l'ère d'Osiris expirera, l'ombre de Seth s'étendra sur nous, mais un grand guerrier nommé Sphinx, l'Élu, surgira pour protéger l'Œil éternel de Râ.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cuando la Era de Osiris llegue a su fin, la Sombra de Set descenderá sobre nosotros, pero un gran guerrero de nombre Sphinx se revelará como el Elegido para defender el Ojo eterno de Ra.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Quando l'Era di Osiride sarà al termine, l'ombra di Set calerà su di noi, ma un grande guerriero di nome Sphinx, emergerà come l'Eletto, in difesa dell'Occhio eterno di Ra.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>오시리스의 시대가 끝날 때, 세트의 그림자가 우리 위로 떨어질 것이다, 하지만 스핑크스라는 이름의 위대한 영웅이 선택 받은 자로 떠올라 라의 영생의 눈을 보호할 것이다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>オシリスの時代が終わったら、セトの影が降りてくる、けどスフィンクスと呼ばれている武士は、ラーの永遠な目を守る為に選ばれし者として現れる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Όταν η εποχή του Όσιρι έρθει στο τέλος της, η σκιά του Σετ θα βυθιστεί πάνω μας, αλλά ένας μεγάλος πολεμιστής με το όνομα Σφιγξ, θα αποκαλυφθεί ως ο Επιλεγμένος, για να προστατεύσει το Αιώνιο Μάτι του Ρα.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>When the Age of Osiris comes to an end, the Shadow of Set will descend upon us, but a great warrior by the name of Sphinx, will emerge as the Chosen One, to defend the Eternal Eye of Ra.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Quando a Era de Osíris chegar ao fim, a Sombra de Set descerá sobre nós, mas um grande guerreiro pelo nome de Sphinx, irá emergir como O Escolhido, para defender o Olho Eterno de Rá.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Complete the Uruk Temple Trial and return what you find to the Urukite.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Complete the Uruk Temple Trial and return what you find to the Urukite.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bestehe die Prüfung des Tempels von Uruk und bringe dem Urukiten, was du dort findest.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Fais le test du Temple d'Uruk et apporte tes trouvailles à l'Urukien.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Supera la prueba del Templo de Uruk y entrega tus hallazgos al urukita.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Completa la prova del tempio di Uruk e poi riferisci all'Urukita.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>우루크 사원 시험을 완수하고 우루크에서 발견한 것을 돌려줘라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ウルクの神殿の試しを合格して、手に入れた物をウルク人に届ける。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ολοκλήρωσε τη δοκιμασία του Ναού της Ουρούκ και επίστρεψε αυτό που θα βρεις στον Ουρουκίτη.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Complete the Uruk Temple Trial and return what you find to the Urukite.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Complete o desafio do Templo de Uruk e retorne o que você encontrar para o Urukite.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Heliopolis and return it to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Heliopolis and return it to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Du musst die Heilige Krone von Heliopolis finden und sie zu Anubis bringen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Retrouve la Couronne sacrée d'Héliopolis et apporte-la à Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Encuentra la Corona sagrada de Heliópolis y devuélvela a Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Devi trovare la Sacra corona di Heliopolis e restituirla ad Anubi.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>헬리오폴리스의 성스러운 왕관을 찾아서 아누비스에게 돌려주어야만 한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ヘリオポリスの聖なるクラウンを見つけて、アヌビスに届かなければいけない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Πρέπει να βρεις το Ιερό Στέμμα της Ηλιούπολης και να το επιστρέψεις στον Άνουβι.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You must find the Sacred Crown of Heliopolis and return it to Anubis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você deve encontrar a Coroa Sagrada de Heliópolis e retorná-la para Anúbis.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture the dogs in Heliopolis Cursed Palace and return them to their owner.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture the dogs in Heliopolis Cursed Palace and return them to their owner.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Fange die Hunde im Verfluchten Palast von Heliopolis und bringe sie ihrem Besitzer zurück.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Attrape les chiens du Palais maudit d'Héliopolis. Remets-les à leur maître.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Captura los perros del Palacio Maldito de Heliópolis y devuélveselos a su dueña.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cattura i cani nel Palazzo maledetto di Heliopolis e riportali al padrone.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>헬리오폴리스의 저주 받은 성에서 개들을 사로잡아 주인에게 돌려주어라.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>ヘリオポリスの呪った宮殿にいる犬を全部掴んで飼い主に返す。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Αιχμαλώτισε τα σκυλιά στο Καταραμένο Παλάτι της Ηλιούπολης και επίστρεψε τα στον ιδιοκτήτη τους.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture the dogs in Heliopolis Cursed Palace and return them to their owner.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Capture os cães no Palácio Amaldiçoado de Heliópolis e retorne-os a sua dona.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your final destiny is to face Set in the devastated world of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your final destiny is to face Set in the devastated world of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Deine letzte Bestimmung ist es, Set in der verwüsteten Welt von Uruk entgegenzutreten.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ta destinée est d'affronter Seth dans le monde dévasté d'Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tu destino final es enfrentarte a Set en las devastadas tierras de Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Il tuo destino finale è affrontare Set nel mondo devastato di Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>너의 마지막 사명은 우루크의 황폐한 세상에서 세트와 맞서는 것이다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>スフィンクスの運命はウルクの不毛な世界でセトと戦うこと。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Το τελικό σου πεπρωμένο είναι να αντιμετωπίσεις τον Σετ στον κατεστραμμένο τόπο της Ουρούκ.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Your final destiny is to face Set in the devastated world of Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Seu destino final é encarar Set no mundo devastado de Uruk.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd><E>

column6:
Set has been hiding in his secret palace while orchestrating the destruction of Heliopolis...

You must find his lair and put an end to his plans...

To find where his secret palace is, you will need to talk to the Hittite village elder. Bring him some whiskey to loosen his tongue.
column7:
Set has been hiding in his secret palace while orchestrating the destruction of Heliopolis...

You must find his lair and put an end to his plans...

To find where his secret palace is, you will need to talk to the Hittite village elder. Bring him some whiskey to loosen his tongue.
column8:
Set hält sich in seinem geheimen Palast versteckt, während er die Zerstörung von Heliopolis dirigiert...

Du musst ihn finden und seine Pläne zerschlagen...

Der Dorfälteste kann dir sagen, wo der Palast ist. Bringe ihm etwas Whiskey, um seine Zunge zu lösen.
column9:
Seth se cache dans son Palais secret pour orchestrer la destruction d'Héliopolis...

Repère sa tanière et met un terme à ses plans...

Pour trouver son repère, parle à l'Ancien du village hittite. Apporte-lui du bon whisky pour lui délier la langue.
column10:
Set está oculto en su palacio secreto mientras planea la destrucción de Heliópolis.

Encuentra su guarida y acaba con sus planes.

Para averiguar dónde está el palacio, debes hablar con el anciano del pueblo de hitita. Llévale whisky para que afloje la lengua.
column11:
Set si è nascosto nel suo palazzo segreto tramando la distruzione di Heliopolis...

Devi scoprire dove si trova e sventare i suoi piani...

Per scoprire dov'è il palazzo devi parlare con l'Anziano del villaggio ittita. Portagli del whisky per farlo parlare.
column12:
세트는 헬리오폴리스의 파멸을 지휘하는 동안 그의 비밀 궁전에 숨어 있었다...

그의 소굴을 찾아서 그의 계획에 종지부를 찍어야만 한다...

그의 비밀 궁전을 찾으려면, 히타이트마을의 장로들과 이야기하여야 한다. 그에게 위스크를 주어 혀가 술술 돌아가게 하라.
column13:
セトは自分の密かな宮殿の中に隠れていながら、ヘリオポリスを破壊する計画を立てる…

彼の居場所を見つけてから彼の邪な計画を止めなければいけない…

セトの密かな宮殿を見つけるには、ヒッタイトの村の長老と話すのが必要だ。彼がお喋りになる為に彼にお酒を上げる。
column14:
Ο Σετ κρύβεται στο μυστικό του παλάτι ενώ σχεδιάζει την καταστροφή της Ηλιούπολης...

Πρέπει να βρεις το άνδρο του και να βάλεις ένα τέλος στα σχέδια του...

Για να βρεις που είναι το μυστικό παλάτι του, πρέπει να μιλήσεις στο γέροντα του Χεττιτικού χωριού. Φέρε του λίγο ουίσκι για να λύσεις τη γλώσσα του.
column15:
Set has been hiding in his secret palace while orchestrating the destruction of Heliopolis...

You must find his lair and put an end to his plans...

To find where his secret palace is, you will need to talk to the Hittite village elder. Bring him some whiskey to loosen his tongue.
column16:
Set tem se escondido em seu palácio secreto enquanto orquestra a destruição de Heliópolos...

Você deve encontrar seu lar e colocar um fim em seus planos...

Para encontrar o local do palácio secreto você precisará falar com o ancião do vilarejo Hittite. Traga-o um pouco de uísque para soltar sua língua.

column6:

King Sobek needs you to deliver a notice of truce to the Mayor of Abydos.
column7:

King Sobek needs you to deliver a notice of truce to the Mayor of Abydos.
column8:
Nachdem Ischkas Plan für einen Krieg zwischen Abydos und Akaria aufgedeckt wurde...

bittet König Sobek dich, dem Bürgermeister von Abydos eine Botschaft zu überbringen.
column9:
Après avoir découvert les intentions d'Ishka qui encourage la guerre entre Abydos et Akaria...

le roi Sobek te charge de donner un avis de trêve au Maire d'Abydos.
column10:
Tras desvelar los planes de guerra de Ishka entre el pueblo de Abydos y Akaria...

el rey Sobek necesita que entregues un comunicado de tregua al Gobernador de Abydos.
column11:
Dopo aver scoperto i piani di Ishka per incoraggiare una guerra fra i popoli di Abydos e Akaria...

Re Sobek vuole che porti una richiesta di tregua al Sindaco di Abydos.
column12:
아비도스와 아카리아 사람들을 부추겨서 전쟁을 일으키려는 이쉬카의 계획을 폭로한 후...

소베크 왕은 네가 아비도스의 시장에게 평화 제안을 전달해주기를 바란다.
column13:
イシカがアカリアとアビドスの戦争を引き起こす為に立てた計画を明らかにした後…

ソベク王が休戦のノートをアビドスの市長に届けるのを頼んだ。
column14:
Αφότου αποκαλύφθηκε το σχέδιο του Ίσκα να ενθαρύννει έναν πόλεμο ανάμεσα στους λαούς της Αβύδου και της Ακάρια...

Ο Βασιλιάς Σόμπεκ σε χρειάζεται για να παραδώσεις μια πρόταση ανακωχής στο δήμαρχο της Αβύδου.
column15:
After uncovering Ishka's scheme of encouraging a war between the people of Abydos and Akaria...

King Sobek needs you to deliver a notice of truce to the Mayor of Abydos.
column16:
Após descobrir o esquema de Ishka para incentivar uma guerra entre o povo de Abydos e Akaria...

O Rei Sobek precisa de sua ajuda para entregar uma nota de trégua para o Prefeito de Abydos.

column7:

Der Arzt lebt am Kanal, der Abydos in die Nord- und Südhälfte unterteilt.
column9:
Le Maire d'Abydos est malade. Va voir le Médecin et tâche de trouver un remède...

Le Médecin vit près du Canal traversant Abydos d'Est en Ouest.
column10:
El Gobernador de Abydos está enfermo. Debes hablar con el Doctor sobre la cura...

El Doctor vive en el canal que divide la zona norte y sur de Abydos.
column11:
Il Sindaco di Abydos sta male. Devi parlare con il medico per trovare una cura...

Il medico vive nel canale che separa il nord e il sud di Abydos.
column12:
아비도스의 시장이 아프다. 치료를 찾는 것에 관하여 의사와 이야기하여야 한다...

의사는 아비도스의 북과 남을 가르는 운하에 살고 있다.
column13:
アビドスの市長は大変病気になった。この病気を治すには、医者と話すのが必要だ…

アビドスの医者はアビドスの北と南を分ける運河の周りに住んでいる。
column14:
Ο δήμαρχος της Αβύδου είναι άρρωστος. Θα χρειαστεί να μιλήσεις στο γιατρό για να βρεις θεραπεία...

Ο γιατρός ζει στο κανάλι που χωρίζει τη βόρεια από τη νότια Άβυδο.
column15:
The Mayor of Abydos is ill. You will need to talk to the Physician about finding a cure...

The Physician lives in the canal that divides the north and south of Abydos.
column16:
O Prefeito de Abydos está doente. Você precisará falar com o Médico sobre encontrar uma cura...

O Médico vive no canal que divide a parte norte e sul de Abydos.

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The higher the defense rating of your monster, the more punishment it can take during battle.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The higher the defence rating of your monster, the more punishment it can take during battle.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Je höher der Verteidigungswert, desto mehr Treffer kann dein Monster im Kampf verkraften.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Plus le degré de défense de ton monstre est élevé, plus il résiste aux coups.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cuanto mejor sea el nivel de defensa del monstruo, mejor resistirá el ataque durante la batalla.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Maggiore è la forza di difesa del tuo mostro, più danni può subire in combattimento.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>괴물의 방어등급이 높을 수록, 전투에서 공격을 더 많이 견딜 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>モンスターの防御力が増えれば増えるほど、対戦で敵の攻撃に耐えられるようになる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Όσο μεγαλύτερη είναι η άμυνα ενός τέρατος, τόσο περισσότερες επιθέσεις μπορεί να αντέξει στη μάχη.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Jo augstāks ir tava briesemoņa aizsardzības vērtējums, jo vairāk tas var ciest cīņas laikā.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Quanto maior for o nível de defesa do seu monstro, maior será sua resistência à ataques durante a batalha.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The higher the attack rating of your monster, the more damage it can inflict on opponents.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The higher the attack rating of your monster, the more damage it can inflict on opponents.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Je höher der Angriffswert deines Monsters, desto mehr Schaden kann es bei Gegnern verursachen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Plus le degré d'attaque de ton monstre est élevé, plus il inflige de dommages.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cuanto mejor sea el nivel de ataque del monstruo, mayor será el daño que infligirá a sus oponentes.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Maggiore è la forza di attacco del tuo mostro, più danni può infliggere agli avversari.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>괴물의 공격등급이 높을 수록 적에게 더 많은 손상을 입힐 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>モンスターの攻撃力が増えれば増えるほど攻撃のダメージが大きくなる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Όσο μεγαλύτερη είναι η επίθεση ενός τέρατος, τόσο μεγαλύτερη ζημιά μπορεί να προκαλέσει στους αντιπάλους του.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Jo augstāks ir tava briesmoņa uzbrukuma vērtējums, jo lielāku kaitējumu tas var nodarīt pretiniekiem.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Quanto maior for o nível de ataque do seu monstro, maior será o dano causado aos oponentes.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This is your monster's health. If your monster loses all of its health, you will no longer be able to release a monster of that type - until you capture another one of course!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This is your monster's health. If your monster loses all of its health, you will no longer be able to release a monster of that type - until you capture another one of course!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Dies ist die Gesundheit deines Monsters. Wenn diese völlig aufgebraucht ist, kannst du kein Monster dieser Art mehr freilassen. Es sei denn, du fängst ein weiteres dieser Art!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>C'est la santé de ton monstre. Quand ton monstre perd toute sa santé, tu ne peux plus lâcher de monstres de ce type - à moins d'en capturer un autre, bien sûr!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Esta es la salud del monstruo. Si el monstruo pierde toda su salud, no podrás liberar de nuevo un monstruo de esta especie, hasta que captures otro, ¡claro!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Questa è la salute del tuo mostro. Se si esaurisce, non potrai più utilizzare un mostro di quel tipo fino a quando non ne avrai catturato un altro.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>이것의 괴물의 체력이다. 만약 괴물이 체력을 다 잃으면, 그 종류의 괴물을 더 이상 풀어놓을 수 없다 - 물론 그 종류의 다른 괴물을 잡으면 가능하다!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>モンスターの体力。モンスターの体力がなくなったら、その種類のモンスターを解放できなくなる。そのモンスターをまた掴むまでにね！<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Αυτή είναι η ζωή του τέρατός σου. Αν το τέρας σου χάσει όλη τη ζωή του, δε θα μπορείς να πλέον να ελευθερώσεις τέρατα τέτοιου τύπου - μέχρι να αιχμαλωτίσεις κάποιο άλλο φυσικά!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Šī ir tava briesmoņa veselība. Ja tavs briesmonis zaudē visu savu veselības līmeni, tu nespēsi izmantot tāda paša tipa briesmoni - protams, līdz ko tu noķer citu!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Essa é a vida do seu monstro. Se o seu monstro perder toda sua vida, você não será mais capaz de soltar um monstro desse tipo - Até que você capture outro, é claro!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You currently have no moves that you can select.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You currently have no moves that you can select.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Im Augenblick hast du keine Moves zwischen denen du auswählen kannst.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tu ne peux pas sélectionner de mouvement.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>No tienes más movimientos para seleccionar.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Al momento, non esistono mosse che puoi selezionare.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>지금은 선택할 수 있는 동작이 없다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>　選択できる動きは何もない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Προς το παρόν δέν έχεις κινήσεις τις οποίες μπορείς να επιλέξεις.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Pagaidām, tev nav neviens gājiens kuru tu vari atlasīt.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você não tem movimentos para selecionar.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You currently have no monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>You currently have no monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Derzeit hast du keine Monster.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tu n'as pas de monstres.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>No tienes ningún monstruo.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Al momento non possiedi alcun mostro.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>지금은 괴물을 소유하고 있지 않다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>モンスターは一匹も持っていない。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Προς το παρόν δεν έχεις τέρατα.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tev pagaidām nav neviena briesmoņa.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Você não tem nenhum monstro.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Acid Darts can be used to dissolve certain heavy metal chains and damage monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Acid Darts can be used to dissolve certain heavy metal chains and damage monsters.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Säurepfeile können bestimmte Metallketten auflösen und Monster verletzen.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Les Flèches acides dissolvent les chaînes métalliques et certains monstres.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>

column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>I Dardi acido possono dissolvere certe catene metalliche e danneggiare i mostri.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>염산 다트들로 특정 금속 사슬들을 녹이거나 괴물들에 상처를 입힐 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アシッドダーツは金属で作った特定の物を溶かしたり、モンスターにダメージを与えたりできる。<ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>An ancient artefact giving the ability to perform a second jump in mid air.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>An ancient artifact giving the ability to perform a second jump in mid air.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ein altes Artefakt, das es einem ermöglicht, mitten in der Luft einen zweiten Sprung zu machen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ancien artefact permettant d'exécuter un deuxième saut en l'air.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Objeto antiguo que puede utilizarse para realizar un segundo salto en el aire.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Un antico manufatto che permette di spiccare un secondo salto a mezz'aria.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>고대의 유물로써 공중에서 이단 점프를 할 수 있는 능력을 부여한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この古代のアーティファクトは空中で二回ジャンプできる能力をあげる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A powerful weapon and tool which fires magical darts at remote targets.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A powerful weapon and tool which fires magical darts at remote targets.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Eine mächtige Waffe, die magische Pfeile auf entfernte Ziele schießt.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Arme puissante permettant de décocher des flèches magiques.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Potente arma y utensilio que lanza dardos mágicos a objetivos lejanos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Una potente arma che lancia dardi magici contro bersagli lontani.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>강력한 무기와 도구로서 원거리의 목표물에 과녁에 다트들을 발사한다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この強力な武器は遠い目標まで魔法のダーツを射撃できる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A magical artifact which allows you to swim under water at great speed.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A magical artifact which allows you to swim under water at great speed.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ein magisches Artefakt, es ermöglicht, mit großer Geschwindigkeit zu tauchen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Artefact magique permettant de nager sous l'eau à toute vitesse.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Objeto mágico que permite bucear a gran velocidad.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Un manufatto magico che ti permette di nuotare velocemente sott'acqua.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>마법의 유물로써 수중에서 고속으로 헤엄칠 수 있게 해준다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この魔法のアーティファクトは水中で素早く泳げる能力をあげる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A magical artifact which allows you to swim under water at great speed.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A magical artifact which allows you to swim under water at great speed.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Um artefato mágico que o permite nadar debaixo d'água com maior velocidade.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>These projectiles magically regenerate, giving you an infinite supply. Can be used to hit targets and certain monsters while swimming underwater.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>These projectiles magically regenerate, giving you an infinite supply. Can be used to hit targets and certain monsters while swimming underwater.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Der Vorrat dieser Munition erneuert sich magisch immer wieder. Damit können Ziele und Monster auch unter Wasser getroffen werden.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ces flèches se régénèrent à l'infini. Elles permettent de toucher certains monstres en nageant sous l'eau.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Proyectiles que se regeneran mágicamente y nunca se agotan. Puedes utilizarlos para golpear objetivos y herir a monstruos mientras buceas.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Questi proiettili si rigenerano magicamente, dandoti una riserva infinita. Possono colpire dei bersagli e certi mostri mentre nuoti sott'acqua.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>이 다트는 마법에 의해 무제한으로 생겨난다. 수중에서 헤엄치고 있을 동안, 과녁과 특정 괴물들을 맞추기 위해 사용된다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この矢は魔法で補充するので、供給は無限だ。水中で目標や特定のモンスターに矢を放つことができる。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>These projectiles magically regenerate, giving you an infinite supply. Can be used to hit targets and certain monsters while swimming underwater.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>These projectiles magically regenerate, giving you an infinite supply. Can be used to hit targets and certain monsters while swimming underwater.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Estes projéteis se regeneram magicamente e nunca se esgotam. Podem ser usados para atingir alvos e certos monstros enquanto estiver nadando debaixo d'água.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>An ancient artifact which imbues you with the strength to push extremely heavy objects.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>An ancient artifact which imbues you with the strength to push extremely heavy objects.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Mit diesem alten Artefakt kannst du extrem schwere Objekte schieben.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ancien artefact te donnant la force de pousser des objets extrêmement lourds.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Antiguo artilugio que aumenta tu fuerza y te permite empujar objetos muy pesados.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Un antico manufatto che ti infonde il potere di spingere oggetti pesantissimi.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>고대의 유물로써 매우 무거운 물건들을 밀 수 있는 힘을 불어넣어 준다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この古代のアーティファクトはとても重い物も押せる力を与える。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>An ancient artifact which imbues you with the strength to push extremely heavy objects.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Um artefato antigo que dá a você força para empurrar objetos extremamente pesados.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>The magical shield used in battle by the great god Osiris.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Der magische Schild, der vom großen Gott Osiris benutzt wurde.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bouclier magique qui protégeait le grand Osiris au combat.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Escudo mágico utilizado en combate por el gran dios Osiris.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Lo scudo magico usato in combattimento dal grande dio Osiride.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>이 마법의 방패는 위대한 신 오시리스가 전쟁에서 사용했던 것이다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>オシリス様が戦闘で使った魔法の盾。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>O escudo mágico usado em batalhas pelo grande deus Osíris.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This magic stone grants the user the power of invisibility... and instant death!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This magic stone grants the user the power of invisibility... and instant death!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Dieser magische Stein bringt dem Benutzer die Macht der Unsichtbarkeit... und den sofortigen Tod!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Pierre magique donnant le pouvoir d'invisibilité... et une mort instantanée!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Piedra mágica que proporciona el don de la invisibilidad... ¡y muerte instantánea!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Questa pietra magica concede il potere dell'invisibilità... e della morte immediata!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>이 마법석은 사용자에게 투명의 힘을 부여한다... 그러나 그 대가로 생명을 빼앗아 갈 것이다!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>この魔法の石は不可視の力を与える…けど急死されちゃう！<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This magic stone grants the user the power of invisibility... and instant death!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>This magic stone grants the user the power of invisibility... and instant death!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Esta pedra mágica garante ao usuário o poder da invisibilidade... e morte instantânea!<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
