column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket is a magical object who can transport items between Sphinx and the Mummy once you have the Book of the Dead.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket is a magical object who can transport items between Sphinx and the Mummy once you have the Book of the Dead.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Tragek-Orb ist ein magischer Korb, der Gegenstände zwischen Sphinx und der Mumie hin- und hertransportieren kann. Dafür wird jedoch das Buch der Toten benötigt.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Khorb-Èye est un objet magique permettant à Sphinx et la Momie d'échanger des objets quand tu as le Livre des Morts.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Kan-Asta es un objeto mágico que transportará cosas entre Sphinx y la Momia si has conseguido el Libro de los Muertos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket è un oggetto magico che può trasportare oggetti fra Sphinx e la Mummia quando avrai il Libro dei Morti.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>바스-켓은 마법의 물건으로 사자의 서를 가지고 있다면 아이템들을 스핑크스와 미이라 사이에서 전송할 수 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket is a magical object who can transport items between Sphinx and the Mummy once you have the Book of the Dead.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket is a magical object who can transport items between Sphinx and the Mummy once you have the Book of the Dead.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Bas-Ket is a magical object who can transport items between Sphinx and the Mummy once you have the Book of the Dead.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Ces-To é um objeto mágico capaz de transportar itens entre Sphinx e a Múmia após você obter o Livro dos Mortos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Coconuts are a favored food of the Urukan lava toad. Lava toads have been known to assist adventurers in exchange for these prized delicacies.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Coconuts are a favoured food of the Spitting Toad. Lava toads have been known to assist adventurers in exchange for these prized delicacies.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Kokosnüsse sind die Lieblingsnahrung der urukischen Lavakröte. Man sagt, dass Lavakröten für Kokosnüsse auch Abenteurern helfen.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Les noix de coco sont le mets favori des Crapauds cracheurs, qui rendent service aux aventuriers en échange de cette délicate gourmandise.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Los cocos son la comida favorita del sapo de lava de Uruk. Se dice que los sapos de lava ayudan a los aventureros a cambio de estos preciados manjares.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Le Noci di cocco sono molto apprezzate dai Rospi sputatori di Uruk, che di norma aiutano gli avventurieri in cambio di queste ghiottonerie.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>코코넛들은 우루크의 용암 두꺼비가 가장 좋아하는 음식이다. 용암 두꺼비에게 이 음식을 주면 탐험가들을 도와준다고 알려져 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Coconuts are a favored food of the Urukan lava toad. Lava toads have been known to assist adventurers in exchange for these prized delicacies.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Coconuts are a favored food of the Urukan lava toad. Lava toads have been known to assist adventurers in exchange for these prized delicacies.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Coconuts are a favored food of the Urukan lava toad. Lava toads have been known to assist adventurers in exchange for these prized delicacies.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Cocos são a comida favorita do sapo de lava de Uruk. Os sapos de lava são conhecidos por ajudarem aventureiros em troca dessas preciosas iguarias.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Atun. Said to be the only means to break the magical Seal of Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Atun. Said to be the only means to break the magical Seal of Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Eine goldene Statue des Gottes Atun. Sie soll der einzige Gegenstand sein, mit dem das magische Siegel von Atun gebrochen werden kann.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Statue dorée du dieu Atun, seul moyen de briser le Sceau magique d'Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Estatua de oro del dios Atum. Se dice que es el único medio para romper el Sello mágico de Atum.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Una statua d'oro del dio Atun. Si dice che sia l'unico modo per spezzare il magico sigillo di Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column12: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>아툰 신의 황금상. 아툰의 마법의 인장을 부술 수 있는 유일한 물건이라 알려져 있다.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column13: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>アトゥン様のゴールドなスタチュー。アトゥンの魔法的な封印を壊すことには、これを使うことしかないと言われている。<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column14: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Atun. Said to be the only means to break the magical Seal of Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column15: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Atun. Said to be the only means to break the magical Seal of Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column16: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Uma estátua de ouro do deus Atun. Dizem ser a única forma de quebrar o Selo mágico de Atun.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Hathor, imbued with magical powers.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column7: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>A golden statue of the god Hathor, imbued with magical powers.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column8: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Eine goldene Statue des Gottes Hathor. Sie besitzt magische Kräfte.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column9: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Statue dorée du dieu Hathor, dotée de pouvoirs magiques.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column10: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Estatua de oro del dios Hathor que posee poderes mágicos.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>
column11: <ES HT_Text_ES_S_BOSStd>Una statua d'oro del dio Hathor, dotata di poteri magici.<ES HT_Text_ES_E_BOSStd>

column6:
Caution! Sphinx uses an Autosave feature.
Insertion of a memory card (PS2) beyond
this point may cause data to be
overwritten. However if you wish to save
your game data, insert a memory card (PS2)
with at least xKB free space.

Press START BUTTON to continue
without saves.
column7:
Caution! Sphinx uses an Autosave feature.

overwritten. However if you wish to save

column8:
Achtung! Sphinx speichert automatisch.
Wenn jetzt eine Memory Card (PS2)
eingesteckt wird, können Daten
überschrieben werden. Zum Speichern wird
eine Memory Card (PS2) mit mindestens
xKB freiem Speicher benötigt.

Drücke die START-Taste, um ohne zu
Speichern fortzufahren.
column9:
Attention! Sphinx dispose d'un système d'Auto-sauvegarde.
L'insertion ultérieure d'une memory card (PS2)
risque d'écraser les données
précédentes. Pour sauvegarder
vos données, insérer une memory card (PS2)
avec au moins xKB d'espace libre.

Appuyer sur la TOUCHE START pour continuer
sans sauvegarder.
column10:
Atención: Sphinx usa la función de autoguardado.
Si insertas una memory card (PS2)
a partir de este punto, puede haber
sobrescritura de datos. No obstante, si deseas guardar
datos del juego, inserta una memory card (PS2)
con al menos x KB de espacio libre.

Pulsa el botón START (inicio)
para continuar sin guardar.
column11:
Attenzione! Sphinx usa la funzione di autosalvataggio.
Inserendo una memory card (PS2) dopo
questo punto si può provocare la
sovrascrittura dei dati. Se vuoi salvare
la tua partita, inserisci una memory card (PS2)
con almeno x KB di spazio libero.

Premi il tasto START per continuare
senza salvare.
column12:
주의! 스핑크스는 자동 저장 기능을 사용합니다.
지금 이후에 메모리 카드(PS2)를 삽입하면
데이터를 덮어써 버릴 수 있습니다.
그러나 게임 데이터를 저장하고 싶으시면
최소한 xKB의 빈 공간이 있는 메모리 카드(PS2)를 꽂으십시오.

저장하지 않고 계속하시려면
START(시작) 버튼을 누르십시오.
column13:
**Caution! Sphinx uses an Autosave feature.
Insertion of a memory card (PS2) beyond
this point may cause data to be
overwritten. However if you wish to save
your game data, insert a memory card (PS2)
with at least xKB free space.

Press START BUTTON to continue
without saves.*
column14:
Προσοχή! Το Σφιγξ χρησιμοποιεί λειτουργία αυτόματης αποθήκευσης.
Η εισαγωγή κάρτας μνήμης (PS2) πέρα
από αυτό το σημείο μπορεί να προκαλέσει την αντικατάσταση
 δεδομένων. Ωστόσο αν επιθυμείς να αποθηκεύσεις
τα δεδομένα παιχνιδιού σου, εισήγαγε μία κάρτα μνήμης (PS2)
με τουλάχιστον xKB ελεύθερου χώρου.

Πάτησε το START για να συνεχίσεις
 χωρίς αποθήκευση.
column15:
Uzmanību! Sfinkss izmanto Autoglabāšanas funkciju.
Ieliekot atmiņas karti (PS2) aiz
šī punkta varētu rast ka dati
pārrakstīti. Bet, ja tu vēlies saglabād
tavus spēļu datus, ieliec atmiņas karti (PS2)
ar vismazt xKB brīvas vietas.

Spied SĀKUMA POGU lai turpinātu
bez saglabāšanas.
column16:
Atenção! Sphinx utiliza a função de autosave.
Inserir um memory card (PS2)
a partir deste ponto poderá
substituir dados salvos. Caso deseje salvar
seus dados de jogo, insira um memory card (PS2)
com pelo menos xKB de espaço livre.

Aperte o botão START para
continuar sem salvar.

column6:
You got the Blowpipe!

The magical darts fired from this powerful tool,regenerate giving you an infinite supply.

The darts can be used to hit remote targets but theyare only powerful enough to damage explosive monsters.

Use to assign the Blowpipe to a button.

Once the Blowpipe is assigned, pressthe button to enter first person mode.

Press to fire.

Keep , , or pressed while moving the left Joy-Con to aim using the gyroscopic motion controls.

Press to exitfrom Blowpipe mode.

column8:
Du hast nun das Blasrohr!

Die magischen Pfeile, die du hiermit verschießt,erneuern sich automatisch unbegrenzt.

Mit den Pfeilen kann auf entfernte Ziele geschossen werden,aber sie reichen nur, um explosive Monster zu verletzen.

Benutze , um das Blasrohr einer Taste zuzuweisen.

Sobald das Blasrohr zugewiesen ist, musst dudie Taste drücken, um in den First-Person-Modus zu gelangen.

Drücke zum Feuern .

Keep , , or pressed while moving the left Joy-Con to aim using the gyroscopic motion controls.

Drücke , um denBlasrohr-Modus zu beenden.
column9:
Tu as la Sarbacane!

Ses flèches magiquesse régénèrent à l'infini.

Si elles peuvent atteindre des cibles distantes, ellesn'endommagent que les monstres explosifs.

Utilise pour assigner la Sarbacane à une touche.

Une fois la Sarbacane assignée, appuiesur la touche pour passer en mode 1ère personne.

Appuie sur pour tirer.

Keep , , or pressed while moving the left Joy-Con to aim using the gyroscopic motion controls.

Appuie sur pour sortirdu mode Sarbacane.
column10:
¡Tienes la Cerbatana!

Los dardos mágicos que lanza este poderoso instrumentose regeneran, por lo que son infinitos.

Puedes usarlos para llegar a blancos lejanos, pero sólotienen potencia para hacer daño a monstruos explosivos.

Usa para asignar un botón para la Cerbatana.

Una vez asignada la Cerbatana, pulsaese botón para activar el modo en primera persona.

Pulsa para disparar.

Mantén pulsado , , o mientras mueves el Joy-Con izquierdo para apuntar con los controles de movimiento giroscópicos.

Pulsa para salirdel modo Cerbatana.
column11:
Hai ottenuto la Cerbottana!

I dardi magici scagliatisi rigenerano all'infinito

e possono essere utilizzati per colpire bersagli lontani, masono in grado solo di danneggiare i mostri esplosivi.

Usa per assegnare la Cerbottana a un tasto.

Quindi, premi il tastoper accedere alla modalità in prima persona.

Premi per sparare.

Tieni premuto , , o mentre muovi il Joy-Con sinistro per mirare usando il sensori di movimento giroscopico.

Premi per usciredalla modalità Cerbottana.
column12:
취관을 구했다!

이 강력한 도구에서 발사되는 마법의 다트는재생성 되어 무한으로 공급된다.

다트는 원거리의 목표를 맞추기 위해 사용될 수 있지만폭발하는 괴물들은 상처 입힐 정도만의 위력을 가지고 있다.

를 이용하여 취관을 버튼에 배당한다.

취관의 배당이 끝나면그 버튼을 눌러 일인칭 모드로 변환한다.

를 눌러서 발사한다.

Keep , , or pressed while moving the left Joy-Con to aim using the gyroscopic motion controls.

를 눌러서 취관 모드에서 나간다.

column14:
Πήρες το Φυσοκάλαμο!

Τα μαγικά βελάκια που απελευθερώνονται από αυτό το ισχυρό εργαλείο,αναπληρώνονται δίνοντας σου απεριόριστη ποσότητα από βελάκια.

Τα βελάκια μπορούν να χρησιμοποιηθούν για να χτυπήσουν απομακρυσμένους στόχους αλλά είναιμόνο αρκετά ισχυρά ώστε να βλάψουν τέρατα που εκρύγνυνται.

Χρησιμοποίησε το για να αναθέσεις το Φυσοκάλαμο σε ένα κουμπί.

Όταν το Φυσοκάλαμο ανατεθεί, πάτησετο κουμπί για να μπεις σε λειτουργία πρώτου προσώπου.

Πάτησε για να ρίξεις.

Κράτησε , , ή πατημένα όσο κουνάς το αριστερό Joy-Con για να στοχεύσεις χρησιμοποιώντας τους γυρισκοπικούς χειρισμούς κίνησης.

Πάτησε για να βγειςαπό τη λειτουργία Φυσοκάλαμου.
column15:
Tu ieguvi Šautriņu Trubu!

Kad maģiskie šautriņi tiek izšauti no šī spēcīgā rīka,tie atjaunojas, nodrošinot tev bezgalīgi lielu daudzumu šautriņu.

Šautriņi var tikt izmantoti lai trāptītu pa attāliem objektiem, bet tie irtikai tik spēcīgi, lai ievainotu sprāgstošus briesmoņus.

Izmanto lai piešķirt Šautriņu Trubu uz kādu pogu.

Kad Šautriņu Truba ir piešķirta, nospiedpogu lai ieietu pirmās personas režīmā.

Nospied lai šautu.

Turi , , vai nospiestu kamēr kustinot kreiso Pults Kloķi lai nomērķēt lietojot žiroskopiskās kustības vadību.

Nospied lai izietno Šautriņu Trubas režīma.
column16:
Você conseguiu a Zarabatana!

Os dardos mágicos atirados por essa poderosa ferramentase regeneram, dando a você um estoque infinito.

Os dardos podem ser usados para atingir alvos remotos mas elessão poderosos o suficiente apenas para causar dano em monstros explosivos.

Use para atribuir a Zarabatana a um botão.

Uma vez que a Zarabatana for atribuída, aperteo botão para entrar no modo primeira pessoa.

Aperte para atirar.

Mantenha , , ou pressionado enquanto move o Joy-Con esquerdo para mirar usando os controles de movimento giroscópicos.

Aperte para sair do modo Zarabatana.
